# Problem Statement

Create a simple library management system where multiple functions are used to perform tasks like adding books, borrowing books, returning books, and checking availability of books in the library.
*Example*
py3
library = Library()
library.add_book("Harry Potter")  # Adds a book to the library
library.add_book("Lord of the Rings")  # Adds another book
library.borrow_book("Harry Potter")  # Borrows a book
library.check_availability("Harry Potter")  # Checks availability of a book
library.return_book("Harry Potter")  # Returns a borrowed book


